# Out painting
        
        1. Need: prompt, frame with image
        2. Put image in frame, leave some empty area
        3. Link them to star rect, AI would paint empty area
Hello! How can I assist you today?
Hello! How can I assist you today?

# ChatGPT
        
        1. Need: prompt
        2. Use arrow tool drag from text to anywhere
        3. Shape with text inside is same as text

# Create image variation

        1. Need: image
        2. Link image to star rect, AI would create image variation

# Create image
        
        1. Need: prompt
        2. Link text to star rect, AI would create image

# Create star rect
        
        1. Select star tool in toolbar
        2. Or press [s] on keyboard
        3. Draw a rect on canvas
